data.description: This beautiful 3 bedroom 2 bath home in Sugarmill will not last long. It is not part of the HOA. This home has laminate in the living areas and two bedrooms, while the kitchen and bathrooms have tile. The kitchen has quartz countertops and a farmhouse sink! Enjoy the outdoors with your fully fenced in backyard. This home is in a convenient location, schedule your showing today! Seller will sod the back yard with an acceptable offer.
